    "causal_summary": "`fanout-run.cjs:884-888` `computeLineageTimeoutMs(lineage)` computes `Math.min(iters  timeoutSeconds  2  1000, 4  60  60  1000)` — the `Math.min` saturates to a hardcoded 4-hour ceiling for any lineage whose `iterations  timeoutSeconds  2` exceeds it, with no CLI flag, env var, or config field to raise it",
